short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Afiseaza tipul vaccinului pentru fiecare centru.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When trying to schedule a vaccination on the national vaccination platform of Romania, it is really hard to tell what kind of vaccine is used in each center, making it difficult to pick a center where to register yourself. This extension adds vaccine type information to the list of vaccination centers.
